    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 td {border: 1px solid #000;}\n.html-preview .a5 {className: a5; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: 48px;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;\">Эр-хотиннинг умумий мол-мулкидаги улушга бўлган мулк ҳуқуқи тўғрисидаги гувоҳнома бериш ҳақидаги ариза</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 318.1163434903px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ариза келиб тушди: </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Ариза келиб тушган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йил</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Мерос иши № </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#14}Мерос иши рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 318.18282548476px;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Нотариус идорасининг жойлашган манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">даги</span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; display: none;\">{#23} хусусий амалиёт билан шуғулланувчи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#18}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га </span><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#24}(</span><span class=\"structures structure-24 structure-25\" style=\"className:24 25; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#24}Давлат нотариал идораси рақами</span><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#24}-сон давлат нотариал идораси)</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Аризачиларнинг яшаш манзили </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Аризачиларнинг рўйхатдан ўтилган уй рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-уйда пропискада турувчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Аризачининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ва </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Аризачи турмуш ўртоғининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">лардан</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 318.18282548476px;\">\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Аризачиларнинг яшаш манзили </span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#15}Ариза тасдиқланган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> куни</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Биз – </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Аризачининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ва </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#11}Аризачи турмуш ўртоғининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">лар </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#16}Аризачиларнинг қонуний никоҳ қайд этилган санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> кунидан бошлаб қонуний никоҳда яшаб келамиз.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Биргаликдаги никоҳимиз даврида орттирилган маблағларга </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Аризачиларнинг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#9}Аризачиларнинг рўйхатдан ўтилган уй рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-уй-жойни сотиб олиб, уни </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Уй-жойнинг олди-сотди шартномасини расмийлаштирган нотариус манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-30\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#30}Нотариус фаолияти тури </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> нотариуси </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#18}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#19}Уй-жойнинг олди-сотди шартномаси расмийлаштирилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> куни </span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#20}Олди-сотди шартномасининг қайд қилинган реестр рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> реестр рақам билан қайд қилинган олди-сотди шартномасига асосан </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#11}Аризачи турмуш ўртоғининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">нинг номига расмийлаштирдик.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси «Нотариат тўғрисида»ги қонунининг 62-моддасига асосан, никоҳимиз давомида орттирилган умумий мол-мулкка, яъни </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Аризачиларнинг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#9}Аризачиларнинг рўйхатдан ўтилган уй рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-сонли уй-жойга нисбатан ҳар биримизга </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#21}Аризачиларнинг ҳар бирига ажратилаётган улуш қисми</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> улушга мулк ҳуқуқи тўғрисида гувоҳнома беришингизни сўраймиз.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">ИМЗОЛАР:</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">1. _______________________________________________________</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2. _______________________________________________________</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Нотариуснинг тасдиқлов ёзуви.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;\">Изоҳ:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: italic;\"> ушбу ариза эр ёки хотиннинг бири томонидан ҳам ёзилиши мумкин.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
